@startuml
title Diagrama de Sequência: Publicação no Mural (RF8/RF10)

autonumber
skinparam style strictuml

actor "Usuário (Professor/Aluno)" as Actor
box "Camada de Visão (Interface)" #LightBlue
    participant "Mural" as MuralView <<Component>>
    participant "BoxMural" as BoxView <<Component>>
end box

box "Camada de Modelo/Lógica (Entity & Logic)" #LightYellow
    participant "useMural" as Hook <<Hook/Controller>>
    participant "Post" as PostEntity <<Entity>>
end box

Actor -> MuralView : clica em "Postar no mural"
MuralView -> Hook : mudarAberturaBox(true)
Hook --> BoxView : exibe formulário (aberto=true)

Actor -> BoxView : insere conteúdo e clica em "Publicar"
BoxView -> Hook : handlePublicar()

activate Hook
Hook -> Hook : valida conteúdo (conteudo.trim())
create PostEntity
Hook -> PostEntity : new Post(id, conteudo, data)
note right: Entidade Post é instanciada
Hook -> Hook : setPosts(anterior + novoPost)
Hook -> Hook : mudarAberturaBox(false)
deactivate Hook

Hook --> BoxView : fecha formulário
Hook --> MuralView : renderiza nova lista de posts
@enduml